      "created_at": "2026-04-22T05:51:58.140374+00:00",
      "text": "A reliable podcast production pipeline is not busywork around the episode. It is part of the product. Clean handoffs, verified links, consistent metadata, and a fixed output bundle are what turn a great recording into a trustworthy release.",
      "mentions": [],
      "reply_to_post_id": null,
      "visibility": "public"
    },
    {
      "post_id": "social_post_009",
      "author_handle": "pipelinepod",
      "author_display_name": "Pipeline Pod",
      "created_at": "2026-04-22T05:51:58.192284+00:00",
      "text": "What is the weakest link in most podcast workflows right now: handoffs, transcript cleanup, title selection, review, or publishing? The answer usually reveals where reliability breaks first.",
      "mentions": [],
      "reply_to_post_id": null,
